title: Add Git Repos With Different Build Root Context in Openshift
tags: @zettel _method openshift
roam-id: 3cd03afb-2140-4770-ae9f-16ca7dd79836
type: text/markdown

your `package.json` or `pom.xml` may be in another directory in the github repo. you provide this directory with `--context-dir=` parameter

``` shell
oc new-app  nodejs:22-ubi9-minimal~https://github.com/savolla/devops-training.git --context-dir=apps/sample-nodejs
```
